          <p>We continuously strive to improve the energy efficiency of our products and manufacturing processes, helping our clients reduce their carbon footprint.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-gray-600/20 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-green-600">Waste Reduction</h3>
